name: Harshit-Shrivastava/WhiZ-Search
description: WhiZ Search is a free extension for Google Chrome.  WhiZ Search displays the search results in a small window inside Google Chrome for the requested product including its cost, rating, reviews (if available), picture, a brief description/configuration and other relevant details. When clicked on the product it directly takes to the page from where the product can be purchased.  Currently we are offering a Beta version which can search for products in the following categories:-  1. Books 2. Mobiles and accessories 3. Computers 4. Cameras 5. Games and Consoles 6. Movies and TV Shows 7. Music 8. Mp3 players and iPods 9. Personal and Health Care 10. Home Appliances 11. TVs and Video Players  Currently the search results are offered based on the following criteria:- 1. Relevance 2. Price (high to low) 3. Price (low to high)
